Process called "check_keywords_D" takes word as Integer returns Integer:
    If string_equals(word, "Display") is equal to 1:
        Return TOKEN_PRINT
    Otherwise If string_equals(word, "Decrease") is equal to 1:
        Return TOKEN_DECREASE
